title: Bitcoin, Ethereum Record Losses; Render Token, Dogecoin Among Top Losers
description: Bitcoin (CRYPTO: BTC) moved lower, but the cryptocurrency prices traded above the key $28,000 level on Friday. Ethereum (CRYPTO: ETH) also moved lower, trading below the key $2,000 mark this morning.
